@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vtbiib(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.cos(0.26)
    v2 = (wp.abs(0.85) / wp.sin(0.45))
    v1 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.45 * v0 + 0.23)) * (wp.cos(v2 + 0.09) / (v2 + 0.00 / v1 + 0.63)))
    v0 = wp.cos(v0)
    v1 = v2
    v2 = ((wp.exp(v1 + 0.18) / (v1 + 0.00 * v1 + 0.79)) - ((v2 + 0.02 / v0 + 0.06) / (v2 + 0.25 * v1 + 0.42)))
    v0 = 0.30
    data[tid] = v0
